.env
.env*
agent-skills/
docs/superpowers/
*.pyc
__pycache__/
.DS_Store
docs/demo-script.md
CLAUDE.md
.claude

# Python virtualenvs
.venv/
venv/

# Terraform — never commit real vars, state, or the provider cache
**/terraform.tfvars
!**/terraform.tfvars.example
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.backup
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.lock.hcl

# Service-account JSON keys (BigQuery, GCS staging). `secrets/` is
# created on `make setup` with a placeholder gcp-key.json. The real key
# replaces that file but must never be committed.
secrets/*
!secrets/.gitkeep

# TPC-H workload — local .tbl outputs (regenerable via `make tpch-data`)
workloads/tpch/data/*
!workloads/tpch/data/.gitkeep

